{ Engine was playing black and wanted to perpetually check even though
  winning. It appears it couldn't gain a material advantage in the
  amount of time it searched, so it kept moving the queen back to e4 }

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Bc4 Nc6 5. Kf1 O-O 6. Ke1 Nxe4 7. Ke2 Bxc3 8. bxc3 d5 9. Bb3 Bg4 10. h3 Bxf3+ 11. gxf3 Qh4 12. fxe4 Qxe4+ 13. Kf1 Qxh1+ 14. Ke2 Qe4+ 15. Kf1 Qh1+ 16. Ke2 Qe4+
